OL,3,CBereaved mother still searching for
OL,4,Canswers six years after baby death
OL,6,FSince the review began more than 2,000
OL,7,Fletters have been sent to families,
OL,8,Fwho may have experienced failings in
OL,9,Ftheir care.
OL,11,FTo date, 1,898 families are part of
OL,12,Fthe review into 412 maternity
OL,13,Fexperiences, led by former senior
OL,14,Fmidwife Donna Ockenden - which
OL,15,Flaunched in 2022.
OL,17,FLeah told ITV News Central's health
OL,18,Fcorrespondent Nancy Cole that
OL,19,Freceiving the letter made her feel
OL,20,F'like someone was listening'.
