OL,3,CBereaved mother still searching for
OL,4,Canswers six years after baby death
OL,6,FShe said: "It was a sigh a relief,
OL,7,Fbecause we knew there was somebody
OL,8,Fthere and that they wanted to listen.
OL,10,F"When I read the letter, I said
OL,11,Fstraight away - I need to do this. I
OL,12,Fneed to not only do this for myself,
OL,13,Fbut for Mason."
OL,15,FLeah wright tells ITV Central it was a
OL,16,F'relief' to get a letter through the
OL,17,Fpost about the Nottingham maternity
OL,18,Freview.
OL,20,FLeah's son Mason was stillborn at 27
OL,21,Fweeks.
