OL,3,CBereaved mother still searching for
OL,4,Canswers six years after baby death
OL,6,FLeah is still unclear what went wrong.
OL,7,FBut for her what is clear, is a lack
OL,8,Fof bereavement care from the trust,
OL,9,Fleft her feeling alone.
OL,11,FShe said: "When I was in hospital I
OL,12,Fwas given a card for a lady who came
OL,13,Fto see me, she told me I could ring
OL,14,Fher when I got out of hospital.
OL,16,F"I tried to get in touch with her
OL,17,Fquite a few times, but there was no
OL,18,Freply. I was on my own basically - I
OL,19,Fhad family, but there was no
OL,20,Fprofessional help."
