OL,6,FSenior midwife Donna Ockenden said:
OL,7,F"Every week a new family or two will
OL,8,Fcontact the review and then we go
OL,9,Fthrough a process with them.
OL,11,F"We still anticipate that we will
OL,12,Fpublish our final review in September
OL,13,Fnext year. I'm confident that we can
OL,14,Fkeep listening to women and keep
OL,15,Freceiving new experiences from women
OL,16,Funtil June next year."
