OL,3,CBereaved mother still searching for
OL,4,Canswers six years after baby death
OL,6,FThe review team are planning a
OL,7,Fgathering in Nottingham on 15 June for
OL,8,Ffamilies to meet other families. This
OL,9,Fwill be the second time they hold this
OL,10,Fkind of event.
OL,12,FNottingham University Hospitals Trust
OL,13,Fhas apologised for failings in Leah's
OL,14,Fcare and has said it would be happy to
OL,15,Fmeet with her to try and help get the
OL,16,Fanswers she's looking for.
