OL,4,Canswers six years after baby death
OL,6,FAnthony May, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FNottingham University Hospitals said:
OL,8,F"I would like to share our sincere
OL,9,Fcondolences to Ms Wright for her loss,
OL,10,Fand of course apologise for any
OL,11,Ffailings in the care she received in
OL,12,F2018.
OL,14,F"It is absolutely right and proper
OL,15,Fthat Ms Wright is part of the
OL,16,FIndependent Review into our maternity
OL,17,Fservices.
